While international travel is on hold, local road trips and holidays are on the up. With our beautiful scenery, cultural history and wealth of fauna and flora, biking holidays are fast becoming a popular choice for families as a way to enjoy the great outdoors together. Once you’ve done the research and found the perfect destination for your bike trip, the hardest part is out the way. Next is to line up all your family’s gear and get packing. * Source: thulestore.co.za